file_content.text: You will be destroyed, intruder!
You accuse us of defective craft. Am I understanding correctly, Gorik-Colonel?
What I'm saying, my dear friends, is that the latest objective was not destroyed.
Geonosian construction is flawless. Any flaws are in your design, not--
Intruders! What do you here? Speak!
We're here to put an end to this operation. Drop your weapons! Now!
Surrender!
Have any other plans you'd like to share with us?
We enjoyed your conversation.
Intruder! What do you here, Zabrak-thing filth?
An intruder! What do you here, human-thing scum?
I'm here to stop you. Lay down your weapons! Now!
Surrender!
I think I overheard everything I needed to hear.
I enjoyed your conversation.
I came to show you what happened to your droids.
Ready to die?
Republic soldiers! Eliminate them, Kyvax--at once!
A Republic soldier! She must be eliminated, Kyvax--immediately!
A Republic soldier! Kill him, Kyvax--now!
Elites, swarm! Attack! Kill!
